I encountered a similar issue when I was unit testing Twilio SMS.

I solved the issue by registering [JavaTimeModule][1] on the ObjectMapper.


```
        String json = &quot;{\&quot;status\&quot;: \&quot;sent\&quot;}&quot;;
        ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();
        mapper.registerModule(new JavaTimeModule());
        var message = Message.fromJson(json, mapper);
```


  [1]: https://fasterxml.github.io/jackson-modules-java8/javadoc/datetime/2.9/com/fasterxml/jackson/datatype/jsr310/JavaTimeModule.html

